title: NYS Ends Religious Exemptions For Vaccinations
description: Religious exemptions for vaccinations are no longer allowed in New York. Gov. Cuomo signed the legislation Thursday, calling the measles outbreak a public health crisis. CBS2's Natalie Duddridge reports.
